    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二大太监",
        "公子吕",
        "再不能祝寿筵兄弟孝顺",
        "叫人来看车辆颖城够奔",
        "可叹你正青春一旦命丧",
        "四太监",
        "四宫女",
        "四御林军",
        "实指望接君位母子同庆",
        "武姜",
        "王后"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四宫女、武姜同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "寄书后我的儿全无音讯，\n这几日只觉得坐卧不宁。\n莫不是小宫奴泄漏书信？\n莫不是京邑中少将缺兵？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子吕上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子吕",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领了君侯命，特地到宫廷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子吕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见国母。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到此何干？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子吕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了君侯之命，有书信一封，请国母观看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见书信不由我心神不定，\n泄漏了机密事难以调停。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿叔段他……他现在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子吕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太叔夫妻俱都自尽了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子吕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫妻自尽了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "猛听得小娇儿夫妻自刎，"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔段！我儿！唉，儿呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "吓坏了年迈人丧胆离魂。\n实指望来膝前侍奉晨昏。\n可叹你抛为娘竟赴幽冥。\n再不能守封疆仍回共城。\n这是我溺爱过枉送儿呀——"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命！我的姣儿呀——"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "肠寸断悔已晚痛杀老身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "实指望接君位母子同庆、可叹你正青春一旦命丧、再不能祝寿筵兄弟孝顺、四宫女",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人死不能复生，请国母保重。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子吕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉君侯之命，请国母驾至颖地行宫居住。君侯发有誓言：不及黄泉，无相见也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，罢了吓罢了！寤生这样忍心，竟将老身贬往颖城居住么？唉，我好苦命也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "死一子别一子又悲又恨，\n一旦间母与子反面无情。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二宫女引王后同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王后",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忽听得众宫娥前来报信，\n怎能够将老母贬出宫庭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见母后。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀媳妇呀，那寤生竟要将为娘贬出宫庭去了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀母后哇！君侯纵有请驾别居之意，不过一时愤怒。母后且休烦恼，待儿媳\n赶往军前，劝谏君侯便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你虽然有此孝心，只是我亦羞见你夫君之面，还是迁往颖地，以了残生便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要留我除非是海枯石尽，\n且到那颖城地苦度光阴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监、四御林军、二大太监自两边分上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四太监、四御林军、二大太监",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣等叩见国母。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四太监、四御林军、二大太监",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉君侯之命，护送国母起程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，你们送我起程？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四太监、四御林军、二大太监",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯何在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四太监、四御林军、二大太监",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯发下誓言，不及黄泉无相见也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寤生！我儿！你好狠的心肠也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "寤生儿发誓言心肠太狠，\n从今后母子们两下离分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "叫人来看车辆颖城够奔、王后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母后一路保重，媳妇不能远送了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武姜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "此一去真好似凤鸟失群。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "摆驾回宫。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
